queness, one that adds to the global momentum of female strength, power and perseverance. He sought the support of this year World Humanitarian Day in honoring those women who have tirelessly improved countless lives, showcasing incredible strength along the way. The lawmaker urged the aid workers not to relent in their duties, saying government is ready to give necessary support in terms of security as promised by both Federal and State governments. Housewife drags ex-husband to court, seeks N1.1m for daughter’s upkeep(Opens in a new browser tab) It would be recalled that United Nations set aside the date to honour humanitarian efforts worldwide and propagate need for support. Vanguard